name: UNOS_CLINICAL_INFO
description: Additional information reported to the United Network for Organ Sharing (UNOS) for each of the registry records or forms.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique ID of the registry record.

columns.name: UNOS_ORGAN_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of organ transplanted.

columns.name: UNOS_CARE_PROV_BY_C_NAME
columns.description: The place or type of provider responsible for the patient's follow-up care.

columns.name: UNOS_CARE_PROV_OTH
columns.description: If different from common answers, the specified place or type of provider responsible for the patient's follow-up care.  This clarifies the answer in the UNOS_CARE_PROV_BY_C column.

columns.name: UNOS_WAS_HOSP_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies whether the patient was hospitalized during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_NBR_HOSP_ADMIT
columns.description: Specifies the number of hospitalizations during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_HOSP_STAT_C_NAME
columns.description: If the number of hospitalizations is unspecified, this field indicates why.

columns.name: UNOS_CLIN_RSCH_YN
columns.description: Specifies whether the patient participated in any clinical research protocols for immunosuppressive medications.

columns.name: UNOS_CLIN_RSCH_SPEC
columns.description: If the patient participated in any protocols for immunosuppressive medications, this specifies which ones.

columns.name: UNOS_DISEASE_RCR_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates the presence or absense of disease recurrence.

columns.name: UNOS_IMM_NONCOMP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether there was evidence of patient non-compliance with immunosuppressive medications that could have compromised the patient's recovery.

columns.name: UNOS_MAINT_MEDS_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies whether maintenance immunosuppressive medications were given during the follow-up period.
entries: Yes, same as previous validated report
Yes, but different than previous validated report
Yes, same as validated TRR form
Yes, but different than validated TRR form

columns.name: UNOS_IMM_DISC_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the physician discontinued all immunosuppressive medications.

columns.name: UNOS_CREATININE
columns.description: The patient's most recent serum creatinine.

columns.name: UNOS_CREAT_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: The reason why the most recent serum creatinine is unspecified.

columns.name: UNOS_ACUTE_REJ_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether there were any acute rejections during the last follow-up period.
entries: Yes, at least one episode treated with anti-rejection agent
Yes, none treated with additional anti-rejection agent

columns.name: UNOS_BX_CONFIRM_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether a biopsy was done to confirm acute rejection.

columns.name: UNOS_MALG_POSTTXP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether any post-transplant malignancies were found during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_MALG_DNR_REL_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether discovered post-transplant malignancies were related to the donor.

columns.name: UNOS_MALG_PRETXP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether discovered post-transplant malignancies were recurrences of a pre-transplant tumor.

columns.name: UNOS_MALG_NOVO_T_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether discovered post-transplant malignancies were new solid tumors.

columns.name: UNOS_MALG_LYMPH_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether discovered post-transplant malignancies were new Lymphoproliferative disease and Lymphoma.

columns.name: UNOS_DIABETES_FP_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies whether the patient had an onset of diabetes during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_INSULIN_DEP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient is insulin dependent.

columns.name: UNOS_CAD_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient was diagnosed with coronary artery disease during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_PASTYR_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any bone fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_SPINE_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any spine compression fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_SPINE_NUM
columns.description: The patient's number of spine compression fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_EXTRM_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any extremity fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_EXTRM_NUM
columns.description: The patient's number of extremity fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_OTHER_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any other fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_FRAC_OTHER_NUM
columns.description: The patient's number of other fractures either in the past year or since the last follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_AVN_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient was diagnosed with Avascular Necrosis (AVN) during the follow-up period.

columns.name: UNOS_PRI_DEATH_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's primary cause of death.
entries: Kidney Graft Failure: Primary Non-Function (Graft Never Functioned Post-Transplant)

columns.name: UNOS_PRI_DEATH_OTH
columns.description: Specifies the primary cause of death for the kidney graft recipient if that cause of death was not picked from a list.

columns.name: UNOS_SEC_DEATH_OTH1

columns.name: UNOS_SEC_DEATH_OTH2

columns.name: UNOS_DIALYSIS_C_NAME

Yes, returned to (or continued on) temporary dialysis

columns.description: The name of the center at which the patient receives dialysis.
